Exhibition “Post Zang Tumb Tuuum. Art Life Politics: Italia 1918–1943”.
Open at .@FondazionePrada in Milan until 25/6/18.
https://t.co/KXPnhP9Oma https://t.co/JyBJxs0u1k

“Post Zang Tumb Tuuum. Art Life Politics: Italia 1918–1943”, currently hosted at .@FondazionePrada in Milan, takes into consideration the contemporary social, political and vital context of the interwar years in Italy through an immersive journey. On view until 25/6/18. https://t.co/7mVVIKabc4

“Post Zang Tumb Tuuum. Art Life Politics: Italia 1918–1943” conceived and curated by Germano Celant, is an exhibition that explores the world of art and culture in Italy in the interwar years. Open to the public at .@FondazionePrada in Milan until 25/6/18.
